The Regular performs well in long text settings, while Light and Bold faces are extremely legible at large sizes. Type family spans 18 faces: 6 Upright with the matching Italics of normal width and 6 Narrow ones. The typeface was designed by Vasily Biryukov and released by Paratype in 2015.
